{"about_the_game":"The free scenario RPG that you create<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u25a0 Basic scenario<br />\r\nSomething is wrong with this world...<br />\r\nAt first glance, it looks the same as usual...a peaceful daily routine...<br />\r\nBut...the world...something is wrong...<br />\r\nWhen I realized the &quot;truth&quot;...the world was already in its &quot;end&quot;...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou are the one chosen to save the world<br />\r\nSee the world.<br />\r\nTravel the world and get knowledges and experience.<br />\r\nThere, learn people, worry about society, and encounter life crises.<br />\r\nEvery experience makes you stronger.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChange the fate of the world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u25a0 Game system<br />\r\n\u00b7battle<br />\r\nEach hero can use &quot;normal attack&quot;, &quot;magic&quot;, and &quot;special skill&quot;.<br />\r\n\u201cMagic\u201d can be purchased at the shop, and can also be obtained by defeating enemies.<br />\r\n&quot;Special skills&quot; were depending on the heroes. When facing a strong enemy, devising the role of the heroes is the point of strategy.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u30fb Help items when fighting enemies is troublesome<br />\r\nA &quot;stealth machine&quot; that will not be encountered for 300 steps.<br />\r\nA &quot;battle skip ticket&quot; that allows you to skip a battle with an enemy you've defeated once.<br />\r\nYou can buy these two at the shop.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u30fbFree scenario<br />\r\nYou are free, from the moment you leave the royal castle.<br />\r\nGo where you want to go and do what you want to do.<br />\r\nIf you get lost in too much freedom, Paris City's &quot;Magician&quot; will show you the way.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u30fb Equipment that gets stronger as you strengthen<br />\r\nIt seems that somewhere in this world, there are &quot;Evolution Sword&quot;, &quot;Evolution Shield&quot;, &quot;Evolution Helmet&quot;, and &quot;Evolution Armor&quot;.<br />\r\nUnlike normal equipment, it becomes stronger the more you strengthen it.<br />\r\nCollect &quot;Strenold&quot; and strengthen your Evolution Equipment.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u30fbNew game with Cleared data<br />\r\nThis game has multiple endings.<br />\r\nIt is possible to play from the beginning while being strong without wasting the elements that have been raised.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2069940?t=1714696615","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2069940?t=1714696615","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2069940/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1714696615","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2069940/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1714696615","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2112030,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"The free scenario RPG that you create<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u25a0 Basic scenario<br />\r\nSomething is wrong with this world...<br />\r\nAt first glance, it looks the same as usual...a peaceful daily routine...<br />\r\nBut...the world...something is wrong...<br />\r\nWhen I realized the &quot;truth&quot;...the world was already in its &quot;end&quot;...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou are the one chosen to save the world<br />\r\nSee the world.<br />\r\nTravel the world and get knowledges and experience.<br />\r\nThere, learn people, worry about society, and encounter life crises.<br />\r\nEvery experience makes you stronger.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChange the fate of the world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u25a0 Game system<br />\r\n\u00b7battle<br />\r\nEach hero can use &quot;normal attack&quot;, &quot;magic&quot;, and &quot;special skill&quot;.<br />\r\n\u201cMagic\u201d can be purchased at the shop, and can also be obtained by defeating enemies.<br />\r\